{
  "stem": "18778.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 376.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I lived with the, the Blums for a whole year because my parents, at the time, had no means of, of keeping me.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother was a domestic in a household.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father, as a lawyer, certainly couldn't pursue his profession here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At the time we arrived here, my father was 58 years old.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was not in good health, and he started out by peddling European-made candy from door to door.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he developed all kinds of contacts that way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Eventually, he got a job as a translating editor with a German newspaper here in Philadelphia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was a very good job for those days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The newspaper was called the And it actually had published here already through World War I and through World War II, until the '50s.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I think it then became a weekly, and eventually it merged with a New York German newspaper called the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know if that's still in existence.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But at any rate, my father worked there until he became too ill to work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My father had a problem that nobody seemed to know what it was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was treated for gallbladder.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was treated for all kinds of theories.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He saw big doctors in Europe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He saw big doctors right here in the United States.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Nobody could figure out what was wrong.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "After he died, we had an autopsy taken, simply because we felt he would have wanted that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it turns out that he had a hiatal hernia that pressed on the heart.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "For years, he would have terrible pains, like a heart attack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he would be able to, sometimes, stop them by a pressure.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And therefore, he never wanted to have any exploratory surgery.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
